{"tid":1184781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門首季經濟收縮3.2%　結束連續十季增長","createTime":"2019-06-04T00:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T14:33:43.000Z","uid":51271,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"90b2b687fbbf349075e94b2ef5691d0fa779494d","tid":1184781,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"澳門經濟下行壓力升溫，統計部門公布今年首季的經濟按年實質收縮3.2%，結束連續十季的增長軌道。<br />\n<br />\n澳門統計普查局表示，主要原因是整體需求轉弱，增長動力不足。當中外部需求明顯放緩。報告指出，雖然入境旅客大幅增加，但消費放緩，令服務出口按年下跌0.3%，當中兩個支柱行業亦出現走勢逆轉情況，博彩服務出口減少0.6%，其他旅遊服務出口減少0.3%，遠低於上季有6.7%和1.4%的升幅。<br />\n<br />\n公布又顯示，首季內部需求亦受固定資產投資大幅減少拖累，按年倒退9.4%。而首季能抵銷部分經濟下行跌幅的是私人消費和政府最終消費，分別增加2.1%和4.1%。當中政府在僱員報酬，增加2.4%，政府購入貨物和服務淨值上升7個百分點。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460801-20190604.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460801-20190604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=60b0f186\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460801-20190604.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c142491e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460801-20190604.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e2a11739449b0d12c04919fcb5de7dbd3f110b26","tid":1184781,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:46:43.000Z","msg":"有無錢派？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n利申：葡藉居港澳人"},{"pid":"69453579bae75f6989c270163343e98b5514122d","tid":1184781,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e2a11739449b0d12c04919fcb5de7dbd3f110b26","tid":1184781,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:46:43.000Z","msg":"有無錢派？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n利申：葡藉居港澳人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:47:30.000Z","msg":"破產應該無"},{"pid":"a92b8d47993dcd0259b2e74d210954cec2ebf7ad","tid":1184781,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":